iting people to action is more effective than dispatching orders"]},{"trad":"請帖","simp":"请帖","pinyin":"qing3 tie3","defs":["invitation card","written invitation"]},{"trad":"請戰","simp":"请战","pinyin":"qing3 zhan4","defs":["to request to be sent into battle; (by extension) to volunteer for a dangerous or arduous task"]},{"trad":"請援","simp":"请援","pinyin":"qing3 yuan2","defs":["to request help","to appeal (for assistance)"]},{"trad":"請教","simp":"请教","pinyin":"qing3 jiao4","defs":["to ask for guidance","to consult"]},{"trad":"請柬","simp":"请柬","pinyin":"qing3 jian3","defs":["invitation card","written invitation"]},{"trad":"請款","simp":"请款","pinyin":"qing3 kuan3","defs":["to request payment (or reimbursement); to invoice"]},{"trad":"請求","simp":"请求","pinyin":"qing3 qiu2","defs":["to request; to ask","request (CL:個|个[ge4])"]},{"trad":"請求寬恕","simp":"请求宽恕","pinyin":"qing3 qiu2 kuan1 shu4","defs":["to sue for mercy","to ask for forgiveness","begging for magnanimity"]},{"trad":"請看","simp":"请看","pinyin":"qing3 kan4","defs":["please see ...","vide"]},{"trad":"請示","simp":"请示","pinyin":"qing3 shi4","defs":["to ask for instructions"]},{"trad":"請神容易送神難","simp":"请神容易送神难","pinyin":"qing3 shen2 rong2 yi4 song4 shen2 nan2","defs":["it's easier to invite the devil in than to send him away"]},{"trad":"請纓","simp":"请缨","pinyin":"qing3 ying1","defs":["to volunteer for military service","to offer oneself for an assignment"]},{"trad":"請罪","simp":"请罪","pinyin":"qing3 zui4","defs":["to apologize humbly","to beg forgiveness"]},{"trad":"請調","simp":"请调","pinyin":"qing3 diao4","defs":["to request a transfer"]},{"trad":"請辭","simp":"请辞","pinyin":"qing3 ci2","defs":["to tender one's resignation"]},{"trad":"請進","simp":"请进","pinyin":"qing3 jin4","defs":["\"please come in\""]},{"trad":"請領","simp":"请领","pinyin":"qing3 ling3","defs":["to apply for (a subsidy, unemployment benefit etc)"]},{"trad":"請願","simp":"请愿","pinyin":"qing3 yuan4","defs":["petition (for action to be taken)"]},{"trad":"請願書","simp":"请愿书","pinyin":"qing3 yuan4 shu1","defs":["petition"]}]